Here We go

322
00:21:45,020 --> 00:21:47,129
Everybody Stand Up!

323
00:21:48,020 --> 00:21:51,060
大家一起戰鬥

324
00:21:53,930 --> 00:21:56,100
內心充滿不安

325
00:21:56,960 --> 00:22:00,070
不過 Keep Your Head Right Up!

326
00:22:01,060 --> 00:22:02,129
To The Sky!

327
00:22:02,130 --> 00:22:06,190
不論何時 不論何地

328
00:22:06,190 --> 00:22:08,980
Just Call Me Anytime!

329
00:22:08,980 --> 00:22:11,120
我一定會幫你

330
00:22:11,120 --> 00:22:15,189
Happy People's In The House!!

331
00:22:15,190 --> 00:22:19,940
一臉酷酷的樣子

332
